text: Building at 23-27 S. Sixth Street is a historic commercial building located at Terre Haute, Vigo County, Indiana. It was built in 1882, and is a two-story, rectangular, Italianate style brick building. It features a cast iron storefront on the first story, tall, narrow segmental arched windows on the second, and a projecting cornice. It was renovated in 1975.
